briefdescription.para: File transfer service implementation using FTP/FTPS protocols.

detaileddescription.para: This service provides file upload and download capabilities using the FTP protocol. It supports both plain FTP and FTPS (FTP over TLS/SSL).
Uses FluentFTP library for FTP operations.
